{"tid":1116172,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"希望連登可以開返個海外香港人台同澳門台","createTime":"2019-04-19T17:35:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T04:57:45.000Z","uid":39181,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"985ef573e9227a8962c1c3d889b6639827549482","tid":1116172,"uid":39181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T17:35:13.000Z","msg":"而海外香港人台，就係方便各位海外香港人互相交流既集中地，好重要的<br />\n特別依家個個都想移民，而且知道外國點可以增強連登仔國際視野，而且的確好多海外香港人都有上連登不論留學定定居，有個集中地始終好啲<br />\n<br />\n開澳門台因為有時啲澳門人成日都黎搞事同香港人鬧交，搞到啲post騎劫晒<br />\n不如開個台畀佢地自己圍威喂，而且佢地又可以有一個自由評論既地方"},{"pid":"1c17e98d02b5953b3d25ef36bcb2abf0265a2b10","tid":1116172,"uid":201414,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T17:43:21.000Z","msg":"冇撚用架 就算開個台俾澳門癲狗 佢地班撚樣照騎劫啲post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12234cfc1c3a02a5f0baf95fba9a5a0893f52104","tid":1116172,"uid":109983,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T18:09:10.000Z","msg":"澳門狗死走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f159f40d8b512ddb3d41b71a4e406b925f1c8a64","tid":1116172,"uid":92680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T18:12:28.000Z","msg":"點解要開比澳門人<br />\n佢地上番澳門高登咪得囉"},{"pid":"41eb24082f40ae1b56e907a1ca08bef20e76037b","tid":1116172,"uid":39181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T18:19:34.000Z","msg":"至少都整個海外香港人台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e4a444567671cbfcd4ca5e88f66045b936603c0","tid":1116172,"uid":11880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:49:32.000Z","msg":"躝啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bcfeee6974cb49e83f4c3e321a6ae61a9e43e71","tid":1116172,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"